Interface PeriodRepository

All Superinterfaces:
org.springframework.data.repository.CrudRepository<PeriodEntity,Long>, org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<PeriodEntity,Long>, org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaSpecificationExecutor<PeriodEntity>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListCrudRepository<PeriodEntity,Long>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListPagingAndSortingRepository<PeriodEntity,Long>, org.springframework.data.repository.PagingAndSortingRepository<PeriodEntity,Long>, org.springframework.data.repository.query.QueryByExampleExecutor<PeriodEntity>, org.springframework.data.repository.Repository<PeriodEntity,Long>
@Repository public interface PeriodRepository extends org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<PeriodEntity,Long>, org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaSpecificationExecutor<PeriodEntity>
Repository interface for managing PeriodEntity instances. Extends JpaRepository for standard CRUD operations.
